<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1437,885,1163]" pageId="14" pageNumber="303">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,262,1065,1091]" pageId="14" pageNumber="303">Note.</emphasis>
A widespread species from the 
<emphasis box="[622,718,1065,1091]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="303">lariciata</emphasis>
species-group (
<bibRefCitation author="Bolte, K. B." box="[897,1024,1065,1091]" pageId="14" pageNumber="303" pagination="1 - 253" refId="ref6918" refString="Bolte, K. B. (1990) Guide to the Geometridae of Canada (Lepidoptera). VI. Subfamily Larentiinae. 1. Revision of the genus Eupithecia. Memoirs of the Entomological Society of Canada, 151, 1 - 253. https: // doi. org / 10.4039 / entm 122151 fv" type="journal article" year="1990">Bolte 1990</bibRefCitation>
) which has been found in north-east 
<collectingCountry box="[151,249,1101,1127]" name="Pakistan" pageId="14" pageNumber="303">Pakistan</collectingCountry>
, northern 
<collectingCountry box="[361,421,1101,1127]" name="India" pageId="14" pageNumber="303">India</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[432,502,1101,1127]" name="Nepal" pageId="14" pageNumber="303">Nepal</collectingCountry>
, northern 
<collectingCountry box="[612,712,1101,1127]" name="Thailand" pageId="14" pageNumber="303">Thailand</collectingCountry>
and northern 
<collectingCountry box="[866,961,1101,1127]" name="Vietnam" pageId="14" pageNumber="303">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Mironov, V. G. &amp; Galsworthy, A. C." box="[974,1305,1101,1127]" pageId="14" pageNumber="303" pagination="167 - 188" refId="ref7335" refString="Mironov, V. G. &amp; Galsworthy, A. C. (2009) A survey of the genus Eupithecia (Lepidoptera, Geometridae) in mainland South East Asia: Part II. Transactions lepidopterological Society of Japan, 60 (3), 167 - 188." type="journal article" year="2009">Mironov &amp; Galsworthy 2009</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Mironov, V. &amp; Galsworthy, A." box="[1315,1376,1101,1127]" pageId="14" pageNumber="303" refId="ref7434" refString="Mironov, V. &amp; Galsworthy, A. (2014) The Eupithecia of China: A Revision. Brill Acad. Publ., Leiden and Boston, 593 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.1163 / 9789004254534" type="book" year="2014">2014</bibRefCitation>
). It is a new species for the fauna of 
<collectingCountry box="[493,564,1137,1163]" name="China" pageId="14" pageNumber="303">China</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
